<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../283/37283.xml">
Edna Ferber</link></novelist>
</dramatist>
</writer>
's <it><musical wordnetid="107019172" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../885/429885.xml">
Show Boat</link></musical>
</it>.</p>
<p>

Devine died of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../539/18539.xml">
leukemia</link> on <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../363/11363.xml">
February 18</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../549/34549.xml">
1977</link>, at the age of 71, in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../827/107827.xml">
Orange, California</link></village>
